  • Classes in com.sri.ai.grinder.sgdpllt.interpreter used by com.sri.ai.grinder.sgdpllt.interpreter 
    Class and Description
    AbstractInterpreter
    A Rewriter based on a TopRewriter, adding the functionality of solving quantified and aggregate expressions with a MultiIndexQuantifierEliminator provided by the implementation of an abstract method.
    AbstractIterativeMultiIndexQuantifierElimination 
    BruteForceInterpreter
    An implementation of AbstractInterpreter using BruteForceMultiIndexQuantifierEliminator.
    SampleInterpreter
    This interpreter will evaluate expressions, but will sample quantifiers instead of using brute force.
    TopRewriterUsingContextAssignments
    A TopRewriter based on another TopRewriter, and adding functionality for replacing expressions by their assignments stored on the context, stored there by AbstractIterativeMultiIndexQuantifierEliminator#extendAssignments(Map newAssignments, Context context).
